name: Etat d'avancement Consultation
query:
select 
	mr.item_code as "Item Code:Link/Item:120",
	mr.ref_fabricant as "Ref Fabricant::150",
	mr.fabricant as "Fabricant::150",
	ifnull(mr.qty, 0) as "Qty Commandé":Float:100", 
	ifnull(mr.rate, 0) as "P.U":Float:100", 
	mr.parent as "Bon de Commande::150",
	mr.supplier_quotation as "Consultation::150"

from
	`tabPurchase Order Item` mr
